msgid "Great Efreeti"
msgstr "グレートイフリート"

#. [unit_type]: id=EoMa_Great_Efreeti, race=eoma_magical
#: Era_of_Magic\units\Summoners\Great_Efreeti.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Great efreet seethe with a fiery rage that manifests itself in the form of "
"their magic’s wake. In bodies of smoldering heat and flames, both militants "
"and civilians have been burnt mercilessly to charred remains and then to "
"ashes by these fervent beings. Settlements are annihilated overnight by a "
"great efreeti, leaving nothing left but smoldering ruins. Little has anyone "
"understood of their intent or anger, but little does it matter to the "
"summoners who drive them forward, making as much use as possible of their "
"blasts of hellfire and ravaging firestorms."
msgstr ""

#. [attack]: type=fire
#: Era_of_Magic\units\Summoners\Great_Efreeti.cfg:81
msgid "destruction"
msgstr "破壊"

#. [unit_type]: id=EoMa_Great_Jinn, race=eoma_magical
#: Era_of_Magic\units\Summoners\Great_Jinni.cfg:4
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Great Jinn"
msgid "Great Jinni"
msgstr "グレートジン"

#. [unit_type]: id=EoMa_Great_Jinn, race=eoma_magical
#: Era_of_Magic\units\Summoners\Great_Jinni.cfg:20
msgid ""
"New summoners learn early on that jinn are much different from the "
"elementals they have summoned from the Abyss. Jinn bear an insatiable thirst "
"for knowledge that will soon cause them to become great jinn. Wiser than "
"their own masters and possessing some fundamentals of summoning, great jinn "
"are treated similarly to humans, if not better for their insight.\n"
"\n"
"Great jinn frequently hold positions of authority, commanding divisions and "
"even having a place of power in councils. Gifted with quick minds, great "
"jinn still search for answers to life’s questions, despite the position they "
"have."
msgstr ""

